Best practices AWS
|| Last update: 15 Nov 2019

* Rotate keys daily

- [[https://github.com/rhyeal/aws-rotate-iam-keys]]

Take the bash scripts from here and rotate keys daily.

* ACM

Renew ACM certs via DNS not email.

- [[https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2017/11/aws-certificate-manager-easier-certificate-validation-using-dns/]]

* Protect s3 bucket

Replicate it in another region under another account with different IAM accounts. The source cannot control it anymore.

- [[https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2017/11/amazon-s3-adds-new-features-for-data-security-and-compliance/]]
